query.S:
SELECT s.ticket_number AS ticketNumber,
s.ticket_serie AS ticketSerie,
CAST(AES_DECRYPT(s.sale_key, '$secretKeyAES') AS CHAR) AS saleKey,
s.success_at AS successAt,
s.seller_id AS sellerId,
s.id_product AS idProduct,
JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(s.hierarchy, '$[1].code')) AS equipment,
JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(s.hierarchy, '$[2].code')) AS saleSiteCode,
JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(s.hierarchy, '$[3].code')) AS officeCode,
s.status AS status,
s.drawing_date AS drawingDate,
sd.lotterie AS idLottery,
LPAD(CAST(AES_DECRYPT(sd.number, '$secretKeyAES2') AS CHAR), 8, '*') AS number,
sd.sign AS sign,
sd.value AS value
FROM Astro.SUPER_STAR_DETAIL sd
INNER JOIN Astro.SUPER_STAR s ON sd.id_astro = s.id_astro
WHERE s.success_at BETWEEN '$dateHistory' AND '$dateGenerated'
AND s.id_product IN ($idProductsBackup)

SELECT * FROM
awards.EVENT_RESULTS where
id_list_event=$idListEvent and id_event_drawing=$idDraw and 
result_confirmed is not
null;

SELECT * FROM
awards.LOTTERY_RESULTS where
id_lottery=$idLottery and
id_lottery_drawing=$idDraw and
winning_number_confirmed is not null;

SELECT
	inc.id_incentive as idIncentive ,
	name,
	description
FROM
	INCENTIVES inc
WHERE
	inc.config IS NULL and inc.type = 1

SELECT
	inc.id_incentive as idIncentive ,
	name,
	description,
	pci.id_product as idProduct
FROM
	INCENTIVES inc
INNER JOIN PRODUCTS_CHANCES_INCENTIVES pci ON
	pci.id_incentive = inc.id_incentive
WHERE
	inc.type = 1 AND
	inc.status = 1

SELECT
DISTINCT 
    PLD.id_product as idProduct,
    L.id_lottery AS idLottery,
    L.name AS name
  FROM LOTTERIES L
  JOIN LOTTERIES_DRAWINGS LD
  JOIN SUBCATEGORIES_LOTTERY_DRAWING SLD
  JOIN PRODUCTS_LOTTERIES_DRAWINGS PLD
ON
  L.id_lottery = LD.id_lottery
  AND LD.drawing_code = SLD.drawing_code
  AND SLD.id_subcategory_lottery_drawing = PLD.id_subcategory_lottery_drawing
WHERE
    SLD.status not in (3,4,5) and
   L.status = 1
   AND PLD.id_product = $idProduct

SELECT
	P.id_product AS idProduct,
        P.product_initials AS productInitials,
        P.name AS name
  FROM PRODUCTS P

SELECT c.ticket_number AS ticketNumber,
c.ticket_serie AS ticketSerie,
CAST(AES_DECRYPT(c.sale_key, '$secretKeyAES') AS CHAR) AS saleKey,
c.success_at AS successAt,
c.seller_id AS sellerId,
c.id_product AS idProduct,
JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(c.hierarchy, '$[1].code')) AS equipment,
JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(c.hierarchy, '$[2].code')) AS saleSiteCode,
JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(c.hierarchy, '$[3].code')) AS officeCode,c.status AS status,
lt.pos_code as idLottery,
DATE_FORMAT(c.drawing_date, '%d/%m/%Y') AS dateDraw,
c.drawing_date AS dateDraw,
LPAD(CAST(AES_DECRYPT(cd.number, '$secretKeyAES2') AS CHAR), 8, '*') AS number,
cd.direct_total_value as totalValue
FROM lotteriesgames.CHANCES c
INNER JOIN lotteriesgames.CHANCES_DETAIL cd ON cd.id_chance = c.id_chance
INNER JOIN lotteriesgames.CHANCES_LOTTERIES cl ON cl.id_chance = cd.id_chance
LEFT JOIN lotteriesgames.LOTTERIES lt ON cl.id_lottery = lt.id_lottery
WHERE c.id_product IN ($idProductsBackup)
AND c.success_at BETWEEN '$dateHistory' AND '$dateGenerated'

SELECT cd.detail_position AS detailPosition,
cd.id_chance AS idChance,
c.ticket_number AS ticketNumber,
c.ticket_serie AS ticketSerie,
cl.id_lottery AS idLottery,
lt.pos_code AS lotteryCode,
LPAD(CAST(AES_DECRYPT(cd.number, '$secretKeyAES') AS CHAR), 8, '*') AS number,
cd.direct_total_value AS directTotalValue,
cd.digits2_total_value AS digits2TotalValue,
cd.combined_total_value AS combinedTotalValue,
cd.digits1_total_value AS digits1TotalValue,
c.success_at AS successAt,
IFNULL (isd.id_element,isd.incentive_value) as idIncentive,
isd.total_value AS incentiveTotalValue
FROM lotteriesgames.CHANCES_DETAIL cd
INNER JOIN lotteriesgames.CHANCES_LOTTERIES cl ON cl.id_chance = cd.id_chance
INNER JOIN lotteriesgames.CHANCES c ON cd.id_chance = c.id_chance
LEFT JOIN lotteriesgames.INCENTIVES_SAIL_DETAILS isd ON isd.id_chance = c.id_chance AND isd.detail_position = cd.detail_position
LEFT JOIN lotteriesgames.LOTTERIES lt ON cl.id_lottery = lt.id_lottery
WHERE c.id_product IN ($idProductsBackup)
AND c.success_at BETWEEN '$dateHistory' AND '$dateGenerated'

SELECT c.id_chance AS idChance,
c.ticket_number AS ticketNumber,
c.ticket_serie AS ticketSerie,
CAST(AES_DECRYPT(c.sale_key, '$secretKeyAES') AS CHAR) AS saleKey,
c.success_at AS successAt,
c.seller_id AS sellerId,
c.id_product AS idProduct,
JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(c.hierarchy, '$[1].code')) AS equipment,
JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(c.hierarchy, '$[2].code')) AS saleSiteCode,
JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(c.hierarchy, '$[3].code')) AS officeCode,c.status AS status,
DATE_FORMAT(c.drawing_date, '%d/%m/%Y') AS drawDate,
JSON_EXTRACT(i.config, '$.event') as idIncentive
FROM lotteriesgames.CHANCES c
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT DISTINCT(id_chance) as id_chance, id_incentive
FROM lotteriesgames.INCENTIVES_SAIL_DETAILS
) isd ON isd.id_chance = c.id_chance
LEFT JOIN lotteriesgames.INCENTIVES i on isd.id_incentive = i.id_incentive
WHERE c.id_product IN ($idProductsBackup)
AND c.success_at BETWEEN '$dateHistory' AND '$dateGenerated'

SELECT m.id_module_mail AS idMail, m.description_module_mail AS email
FROM collected.MODULE_MAIL m
WHERE m.id_module_mail IN ( $idEmails )

SELECT p.id_commission_category AS idCommissionCategory
FROM POINTS_OF_SALE p
WHERE id_point_of_sale = $idPos
SELECT e.code AS codeEquipment, e.id_equipment idEquipment FROM hierarchies.EQUIPMENTS e WHERE e.id_equipment IN ($idEquipmen)

SELECT homologated_point_of_sale_id, homologated_equipment_id
FROM hierarchies.HOMOLOGATED_DATA
WHERE status = 1 
AND (id_point_of_sale= $idPos OR id_point_of_sale= 0) 
AND (id_equipment = $idEquipment OR id_equipment = 0)
AND id_product = $idProduct

SELECT ld.id_lottery AS idldottery,
ld.drawing_code AS drawingCode,
ld.drawing_date AS drawingDate,
ld.close_date AS closeDate,
ld.created_at AS createdAt,
ld.updated_at AS updatedAt,
ld.draw_id AS drawId
FROM lotteriesgames.LOTTERIES_DRAWINGS ld
WHERE ld.draw_id IN ($drawingCodes)

SELECT sd.id_subcategory as idSubCategory,
lt.close_hour AS closeHour,
lt.drawing_hour AS drawingHour,
ld.drawing_date as drawingDate
FROM lotteriesgames.SUBCATEGORIES_LOTTERY_DRAWING sd
INNER JOIN lotteriesgames.LOTTERIES_DRAWINGS ld ON sd.drawing_code = ld.drawing_code
INNER JOIN lotteriesgames.LOTTERY_TIME_ZONE lt ON sd.id_lottery_time_zone = lt.id_lottery_time_zone
WHERE sd.id_subcategory IN ($idSubCategories) AND ld.drawing_date >= DATE(NOW())
AND lt.close_hour > '$closeHour'
GROUP BY sd.id_subcategory, lt.close_hour
ORDER BY ld.drawing_date, lt.close_hour

SELECT hd.id_holiday AS idHoliday,
hd.holiday_date AS holidayDate
FROM lotteriesgames.HOLIDAYS hd
WHERE hd.holiday_date = '$date'

SELECT
LT.id_lottery as idLottery,
LT.name,
LT.pos_code AS posCode
FROM lotteriesgames.LOTTERIES LT
WHERE LT.id_lottery in ($idLotteries)

SELECT
c.ticket_number as ticketNumber, c.ticket_serie as ticketSerie, c.sale_key as saleKey, c.success_at as successAt,
c.seller_id as sellerId, c.id_product as idProduct, c.equipment as equipment, c.hierarchy as hierarchy, c.status as status,
cl.id_lottery as idLottery, c.date_draw as dateDraw, AES_DECRYPT(cl.number, '$secretKeyAES') as number,  c.total_value as totalValue
FROM millonario.CHANCES_DETAIL_MILLONARIO cl
INNER JOIN millonario.CHANCES_MILLONARIO c ON cl.id_Chance = c.id_Chance
AND c.id_product IN ($idProductsBackup)
AND c.success_at BETWEEN '$dateHistory'  AND '$dateGenerated'
AND cl.id_draw = '$drawId'

SELECT id_papelery_type as idPapeleryType, description, number_width as numberWidth, total_number_printing_lines as totalNumberPrintingLines, status, size_font as sizeFont
FROM PAPELERY_TYPES pt;

SELECT pf.id_print_formats as idPrintFormats, pf.name, pf.state, pt.description as papeleryTypeName, tt.name as technologyTypeName, pf.created_at as createdAt, pf.updated_at as updatedAt, pft.id_sub_category as idSubCategory, pft.id_product as idProduct
FROM PRINT_FORMATS pf
INNER JOIN PRINT_FORMATS_TECHNOLOGY pft ON pft.id_print_formats = pf.id_print_formats
INNER JOIN PAPELERY_TYPES pt ON pt.id_papelery_type  = pft.id_papelery_type
INNER JOIN TECHNOLOGY_TYPES tt ON tt.id_technology_type = pft.id_technology_type
SELECT  id_product AS idProduct, id_print_formats AS idPrintFormats FROM papelery.PRINT_FORMATS_TECHNOLOGY where id_product =  $idProduct

SELECT pf.id_print_formats as idPrintFormats, pf.name, pf.state, pt.description as papeleryTypeName, p.name as productName, p.num_ticket as numTicket, tt.name as technologyTypeName, pf.created_at as createdAt, pf.updated_at as updatedAt
FROM PRINT_FORMATS pf
INNER JOIN PRINT_FORMATS_TECHNOLOGY pft ON pft.id_print_formats = pf.id_print_formats
INNER JOIN PAPELERY_TYPES pt ON pt.id_papelery_type  = pft.id_papelery_type
INNER JOIN PRODUCTS p ON p.id_product = pft.id_product
INNER JOIN TECHNOLOGY_TYPES tt ON tt.id_technology_type = pft.id_technology_type

queryCount.S:
SELECT COUNT(idPrintFormats) FROM (SELECT pf.id_print_formats as idPrintFormats, pf.name, pf.state, pt.description as papeleryTypeName, p.name as productName, tt.name as technologyTypeName
FROM PRINT_FORMATS pf
INNER JOIN PRINT_FORMATS_TECHNOLOGY pft ON pft.id_print_formats = pf.id_print_formats
INNER JOIN PAPELERY_TYPES pt ON pt.id_papelery_type  = pft.id_papelery_type
INNER JOIN PRODUCTS p ON p.id_product = pft.id_product
INNER JOIN TECHNOLOGY_TYPES tt ON tt.id_technology_type = pft.id_technology_type
GROUP BY pf.id_print_formats) as formats

query.S:
SELECT id_product as idProduct, name, num_ticket as numTicket, product_initials as productInitials, created_at as createdAt, updated_at as updatedAt 
FROM PRODUCTS WHERE status = 1

SELECT id_technology_type AS idTechnologyType, name, description, created_at as createdAt, updated_at as updatedAt, driver
FROM TECHNOLOGY_TYPES

SELECT id_product , minimum_transaction_value ,maximum_transaction_value ,
multiple FROM PRODUCT_TOPS pt WHERE id_product = $idProduct AND status=1

SELECT id_product, id_sub_category, id_provider, product_provider_code, name, description, icon, status, created_at, updated_at, product_initials, `position`, url, iva_tax, bills, bills_sequence, num_ticket
FROM products.PRODUCTS

SELECT id_sub_category AS idSubCategory, name
FROM products.SUB_CATEGORIES

SELECT
	p.id_sub_category as idSubCategory
FROM
	PRODUCTS p
where
	p.product_initials = 'CHA'

SELECT id_types, name, status
FROM products.ID_TYPES

SELECT id_product AS idProduct, id_provider AS idProvider, iva_tax AS ivaTax, product_provider_code AS productProviderCode, name AS name, product_initials AS productInitials, status AS status, bills AS bills, bills_sequence AS billsSequence, num_ticket AS numTicket, id_sub_category AS idSubCategory, apply_beps AS applyBeps FROM products.PRODUCTS where id_product = $idProduct

SELECT id_product AS idProduct, id_sub_category, id_provider, product_provider_code, name, description, icon, status, created_at, updated_at, product_initials, position, url, iva_tax, bills, bills_sequence, num_ticket
FROM products.PRODUCTS
where id_sub_category IN ($idSubCategories)

SELECT pa.id_package AS idPackage, pa.package_provider_code AS packageProviderCode, pa.name AS packageName, pa.price AS price, p.id_product AS idProduct, p.id_provider AS idProvider, p.product_provider_code AS productProviderCode, p.iva_tax AS ivaTax, p.name AS productName, p.num_ticket AS numTicket, p.product_initials AS productInitials, pr.provider_code AS providerCode, pa.status AS status FROM products.PACKAGES pa INNER JOIN products.PRODUCTS p ON pa.id_product = p.id_product INNER JOIN products.PROVIDERS  pr ON p.id_provider = pr.id_provider WHERE pa.id_package = $idPackage

SELECT p.id_product AS idProduct,
p.id_provider AS idProvider,
p.product_provider_code AS productProviderCode,
p.iva_tax AS ivaTax,
p.name AS productName,
p.product_initials AS productInitials,
p.status AS status,
pr.provider_code AS providerCode,
p.num_ticket AS numTicket 
FROM products.PRODUCTS p 
INNER JOIN products.PROVIDERS pr ON p.id_provider = pr.id_provider
WHERE id_product = $idProduct

SELECT rs.consecutive_jsa AS consecutiveJsa,
rs.jsa_series AS jsaSeries,
CAST(AES_DECRYPT(rs.sale_key, '$secretKeyAES') AS CHAR) AS saleKey,
rs.sale_date AS saleDate,
rs.seller_user_code AS sellerId,
rs.product_code AS idProduct,
rs.team_code AS teamCode,
rs.sales_site_code AS salesSiteCode,
rs.office_code AS officeCode,
rs.state_code AS stateCode,
rd.draw_id AS drawId,
rd.id_lottery AS idLottery,
LPAD(CAST(AES_DECRYPT(rd.number, '$secretKeyAES2') AS CHAR), 8, '
') AS number,
rd.total_value_pay AS totalValuePay,
LPAD(rc.series, 3, '
') AS serie
FROM raffles.RAFFLES_SALES_DETAILS rd
INNER JOIN raffles.RAFFLES_SALES rs ON rd.id_raffle_sale = rs.id_raffle_sale
INNER JOIN raffles.RAFFLES_CONFIG rc ON rs.raffle_code = rc.id_raffle
WHERE rs.product_code IN ($idProductsBackup)
AND rs.sale_date BETWEEN '$dateHistory' AND '$dateGenerated'

SELECT ps.id_product AS idProduct,
ps.id_user AS idUser,
ps.fixed_commission AS fixedCommission,
ps.variable_commission AS variableCommission
FROM payments.PRODUCT_SELLERS ps
WHERE ps.id_product IN ($idProducts)
AND ps.id_user IN ($idUsers)

SELECT s.idp_id AS sellerId,
s.identification_number AS identificationNumber,
s.email AS email,
s.identification_exp_date AS expeditionDate,
s.address AS address, s.born_date AS birthdate,
s.gender_id AS gender,
s.first_name AS firstName,
s.second_name AS secondName,s.first_surname AS firstSurname,
s.office_id AS idOffice,
s.second_surname AS secondSurname,
s.phone_number AS phoneNumber
FROM sellers.SELLERS s
WHERE s.idp_id IN ($idSellers)

SELECT s.id_commission_category AS idCommissionCategory, s.contract_type_id AS idContractType
FROM sellers.SELLERS s
WHERE s.idp_id ='$idSeller' LIMIT 1

SELECT s.idp_id AS vendedor_codigo, 
CONCAT(s.first_name, ' ', s.first_surname) as vendedor_nombre
FROM sellers.SELLERS s
WHERE s.id_commission_category= '$idCommisionCategory'

SELECT s.idp_id AS id
FROM sellers.SELLERS s
WHERE s.contract_type_id= '$idContractActivity'

SELECT id_product AS idProduct, id_sub_category, id_provider, product_provider_code, name, description, icon, status, created_at, updated_at, product_initials, position, url, iva_tax, bills, bills_sequence, num_ticket
FROM products.PRODUCTS
WHERE id_sub_category IN ($idSubCategories)
